{
  "scene1_1_0": {
    "duration": 3.024,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene1/01_正文_0.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene1",
    "order": 1,
    "subOrder": 0,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "刷小红书，感觉年轻人人均爱马仕"
  },
  "scene1_1_1": {
    "duration": 3.312,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene1/01_正文_1.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene1",
    "order": 1,
    "subOrder": 1,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "逛知乎，感觉应届生起步年薪百万"
  },
  "scene1_2_0": {
    "duration": 1.98,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene1/02_正文_0.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene1",
    "order": 2,
    "subOrder": 0,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "你是不是也产生过这种错觉："
  },
  "scene1_2_1": {
    "duration": 2.196,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene1/02_正文_1.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene1",
    "order": 2,
    "subOrder": 1,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "“原来全世界只有我这么穷？”"
  },
  "scene1_3_0": {
    "duration": 1.26,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene1/03_正文_0.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene1",
    "order": 3,
    "subOrder": 0,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "别焦虑"
  },
  "scene1_3_1": {
    "duration": 2.088,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene1/03_正文_1.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene1",
    "order": 3,
    "subOrder": 1,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "这可能不是你的问题，而是"
  },
  "scene1_3_2": {
    "duration": 1.872,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene1/03_正文_2.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene1",
    "order": 3,
    "subOrder": 2,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "“样本偏差”在作祟"
  },
  "scene1_4_0": {
    "duration": 2.88,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene1/04_正文_0.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene1",
    "order": 4,
    "subOrder": 0,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "今天我们聊聊统计素养的核心"
  },
  "scene1_4_1": {
    "duration": 3.888,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene1/04_正文_1.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene1",
    "order": 4,
    "subOrder": 1,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "即：被调查的那拨人，真的能代表所有人吗"
  },
  "scene2_1_0": {
    "duration": 2.268,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene2/01_正文_0.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene2",
    "order": 1,
    "subOrder": 0,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "想看穿一份调查报告"
  },
  "scene2_1_1": {
    "duration": 3.6,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene2/01_正文_1.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene2",
    "order": 1,
    "subOrder": 1,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "你只需要像拿着放大镜一样，盯着那个“漏斗”看："
  },
  "scene2_2_0": {
    "duration": 1.8,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene2/02_正文_0.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene2",
    "order": 2,
    "subOrder": 0,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "样本是怎么选的"
  },
  "scene2_2_1": {
    "duration": 1.188,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene2/02_正文_1.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene2",
    "order": 2,
    "subOrder": 1,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "够随机吗"
  },
  "scene2_2_2": {
    "duration": 1.692,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene2/02_正文_2.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene2",
    "order": 2,
    "subOrder": 2,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "样本量够大吗"
  },
  "scene2_3_0": {
    "duration": 1.8,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene2/03_正文_0.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene2",
    "order": 3,
    "subOrder": 0,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "记住这个万能金句："
  },
  "scene2_3_1": {
    "duration": 3.312,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene2/03_正文_1.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene2",
    "order": 3,
    "subOrder": 1,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "“这个调查是在哪里做的,到底问了谁？”"
  },
  "scene2_4_0": {
    "duration": 3.924,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene2/04_正文_0.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene2",
    "order": 4,
    "subOrder": 0,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "接下来，带你看穿四个最常见的“统计陷阱”"
  },
  "scene3_1_0": {
    "duration": 4.536,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene3/01_正文_0.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene3",
    "order": 1,
    "subOrder": 0,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "点外卖时，看到一家网红店评分4.9，全是好评"
  },
  "scene3_1_1": {
    "duration": 3.096,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene3/01_正文_1.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene3",
    "order": 1,
    "subOrder": 1,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "结果点回来一吃——难吃得想哭"
  },
  "scene3_2_0": {
    "duration": 1.872,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene3/02_正文_0.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene3",
    "order": 2,
    "subOrder": 0,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "这就是“自选择偏差”"
  },
  "scene3_2_1": {
    "duration": 3.96,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene3/02_正文_1.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene3",
    "order": 2,
    "subOrder": 1,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "仔细看，评论区是不是写着“好评返现3元”"
  },
  "scene3_3_0": {
    "duration": 2.7,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene3/03_正文_0.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene3",
    "order": 3,
    "subOrder": 0,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "为了拿红包的人才会积极评价"
  },
  "scene3_3_1": {
    "duration": 4.464,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene3/03_正文_1.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene3",
    "order": 3,
    "subOrder": 1,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "而那些觉得难吃的人，往往直接拉黑，根本懒得发声"
  },
  "scene3_4_0": {
    "duration": 3.744,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene3/04_正文_0.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene3",
    "order": 4,
    "subOrder": 0,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "我们需要警惕：那些“沉默的大多数”到底怎么想"
  },
  "scene4_1_0": {
    "duration": 1.548,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene4/01_正文_0.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene4",
    "order": 1,
    "subOrder": 0,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "经常听人感叹："
  },
  "scene4_1_1": {
    "duration": 3.852,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene4/01_正文_1.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene4",
    "order": 1,
    "subOrder": 1,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "“现在的华语乐坛不行了，还是以前的老歌好听。”"
  },
  "scene4_2_0": {
    "duration": 4.536,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene4/02_正文_0.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene4",
    "order": 2,
    "subOrder": 0,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "真不是以前没烂歌，而是因为难听的歌早被时间淘汰了"
  },
  "scene4_2_1": {
    "duration": 3.204,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene4/02_正文_1.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene4",
    "order": 2,
    "subOrder": 1,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "能流传到今天、让你在耳机里听到的"
  },
  "scene4_2_2": {
    "duration": 2.232,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene4/02_正文_2.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene4",
    "order": 2,
    "subOrder": 2,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "全是“幸存”下来的神作"
  },
  "scene4_3_0": {
    "duration": 1.908,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene4/03_正文_0.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene4",
    "order": 3,
    "subOrder": 0,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "这就是“幸存者偏差”"
  },
  "scene5_1_0": {
    "duration": 1.296,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene5/01_正文_0.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene5",
    "order": 1,
    "subOrder": 0,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "再看个扎心的："
  },
  "scene5_1_1": {
    "duration": 5.364,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene5/01_正文_1.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene5",
    "order": 1,
    "subOrder": 1,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "老师让学生实名填写教学质量调查表，结果收上来全是满分"
  },
  "scene5_1_2": {
    "duration": 2.376,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene5/01_正文_2.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene5",
    "order": 1,
    "subOrder": 2,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "老师高兴了，学生却无语了"
  },
  "scene5_2_0": {
    "duration": 0.936,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene5/02_正文_0.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene5",
    "order": 2,
    "subOrder": 0,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "为什么？"
  },
  "scene5_2_1": {
    "duration": 3.996,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene5/02_正文_1.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene5",
    "order": 2,
    "subOrder": 1,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "因为在“实名制”的压力下，真实的想法被压抑了"
  },
  "scene5_2_2": {
    "duration": 1.98,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene5/02_正文_2.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene5",
    "order": 2,
    "subOrder": 2,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "这就是“应答偏差”"
  },
  "scene5_3_0": {
    "duration": 3.672,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene5/03_正文_0.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene5",
    "order": 3,
    "subOrder": 0,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "如果换成匿名调查，结果还会这么完美吗"
  },
  "scene6_1_0": {
    "duration": 4.212,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene6/01_正文_0.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene6",
    "order": 1,
    "subOrder": 0,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "最后，某明星超话发起投票：“哥哥的新剧好看吗？”"
  },
  "scene6_1_1": {
    "duration": 2.52,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene6/01_正文_1.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene6",
    "order": 1,
    "subOrder": 1,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "结果99.9%投了“神作”"
  },
  "scene6_2_0": {
    "duration": 4.176,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene6/02_正文_0.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene6",
    "order": 2,
    "subOrder": 0,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "这叫“便利抽样”，也叫“在回音壁里找共鸣”"
  },
  "scene6_3_0": {
    "duration": 3.6,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene6/03_正文_0.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene6",
    "order": 3,
    "subOrder": 0,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "在粉丝圈子里找评价，本身就自带滤镜"
  },
  "scene6_3_1": {
    "duration": 2.988,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene6/03_正文_1.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene6",
    "order": 3,
    "subOrder": 1,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "得出的结论必然是碾压式的好评"
  },
  "scene7_1_0": {
    "duration": 0.936,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene7/01_正文_0.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene7",
    "order": 1,
    "subOrder": 0,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "所以"
  },
  "scene7_1_1": {
    "duration": 4.14,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene7/01_正文_1.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene7",
    "order": 1,
    "subOrder": 1,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "下次再看到那些让你焦虑、让你震惊的统计数据"
  },
  "scene7_1_2": {
    "duration": 1.512,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene7/01_正文_2.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene7",
    "order": 1,
    "subOrder": 2,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "先别急着相信"
  },
  "scene7_1_3": {
    "duration": 2.916,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene7/01_正文_3.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene7",
    "order": 1,
    "subOrder": 3,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "样本无代表性，则结论不可信"
  },
  "scene7_2_0": {
    "duration": 3.816,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene7/02_正文_0.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene7",
    "order": 2,
    "subOrder": 0,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "多问一句：“调查问了谁？是怎么问的？”"
  },
  "scene7_3_0": {
    "duration": 3.168,
    "file": "/audio/statistic_1/scene7/03_正文_0.mp3",
    "sceneId": "scene7",
    "order": 3,
    "subOrder": 0,
    "type": "正文",
    "text": "保持清醒，别让偏见伪装成真相"
  }
}